    q: "Do you service Frigidaire in Sherman Oaks, the Inland Empire, and other parts of SoCal?",
    a: "Yes, Frigidaire is well-distributed across our 5-county service area, with concentrations in production-builder homes throughout the Inland Empire (Rancho Cucamonga, Fontana, Ontario, Moreno Valley) and rental properties across LA. The freezer category specifically (FFFH chest freezers, FFFC stand-up freezers, FFFU upright freezers) is heavily installed in inland garages, and inland garage-installed freezers see harder service life from summer ambient stress (temps in unconditioned garages routinely exceed 100°F in July-August, well outside spec for many freezer designs). Sherman Oaks, Studio City, and the broader San Fernando Valley single-family market also runs strong Frigidaire installations. The 8-branch dispatch grid in the hero CTA shows the closest dispatch territory for any address."
