        <p>FFRE electric, FFRG gas. Standard thermal-fuse + heating element + belt service tree. EF1 condenser dryer code on selected models.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Dishwashers</h3>
        <p class="model-list">FFBD2406NS · FGBD2438PF · FFCD2418US · GLDB957JS · FPID2497RF</p>
        <p>FFBD value-tier (control panel year 6-8 weakness), FGBD Gallery, FPID Professional. Drain pump and water inlet valve are standard wear items.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
        <h3>Ranges, Gas &amp; Electric</h3>
        <p class="model-list">FFGF3054TS · FFEF3054TS · FGGF3036TF · FGEF3036TF · FPGF3077QF</p>
        <p>FFGF / FFEF base, FGGF / FGEF Gallery, FPGF Professional. Surface igniter and bake element work dominate service mix.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="model-card">
